,"content":"  participants?: string[]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":401,"content":"**角色真源**仅 `data/characters/<agentId>.json`。「本包用到谁」由 `cards[].ownerAgentId`、effects 内 `agentId`、attach 目标归属等**派生**，**禁止**把 `participants` 当白名单或作者手维护清单。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":408,"content":"### 8.1 Schedule 落盘分工（钉死）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":412,"content":"| 角色日常 / 周期性外呼目标 | `data/characters/schedule-cards/<cardId>.s-card.json` | `__schedule__` | 角色库 / 专用路径（Studio `POST /api/schedule-cards`） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":417,"content":"1. `schedule_recurring_call` 的目标**只**认 `scheduleCardId` → `characters/schedule-cards/`，或 `cardId` + `packageId=__schedule__`（同目录）；可选 `__free__` 下 free/schedule fallback。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":420,"content":"4. 画布把卡改成 `cardKind=schedule` 仍写回**本包** `cards/`（剧情节点）；日常调度卡必须走 schedule-cards 专用创建口，不得只靠改 cardKind「伪装」。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/需求/13-工具与能力注册.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":118,"content":"| `schedule_recurring_call` | 登记重复外呼 | 每天/每周定时外呼（旧 corn） | `topic_hint`, `hour`(0–23), `minute`, `schedule_mode`:`daily`\\|`weekly`；weekly 要 `weekdays`；可选 `job_id` | Effect `schedule_recurring_call` → `ScheduledIntent.kind: \"recurring\"`；壳 Sink 执行真定时 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/需求/14-资源与媒体资产.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":14,"content":"data/assets/","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":21,"content":"| `data/assets/meta/` | `AssetMeta` 真源 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":30,"content":"  /** 相对 data/assets/ 或 workspace 可解析路径 */","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":59,"content":"- 独立资源台或画布左侧：增删改**全局**资产元数据；文件写入 `data/assets/files/`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]}],"totalLines":17,"totalMatchedLines"